description: About 500 hours of video and audio secretly recorded during meetings of abortion providers will remain under court-ordered seal -- for now. After hearing arguments Friday, U.S. District Judge William Orrick did not rule on the National Abortion Federation's request for a preliminary injunction...
title: Covert Planned Parenthood tapes remain sealed, for now
